er rollerballs’ points, which produce wetter, thicker lines.</p><p>Although the Precise V5 RT doesn’t dry as quickly as the Jetstream, and therefore can smudge (not ideal for lefties), it performs well on most paper. It’s also the least expensive pen we recommend, on a per-pen basis.</p><p><strong>Style:</strong> rollerball<br/><strong>Tip width tested:</strong> 0.5 mm<br/><strong>Widths available:</strong> <a class="product-link" href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/5541/15770/4/78076/?merchant=Amazon" rel="sponsored noopener" target="_blank" data-gtm-trigger="product_link" data-store="Amazon" data-pick-type-id="5" data-vars-outbound-link="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/5541/15770/4/78076/?merchant=Amazon" data-vars-store="Amazon" data-gtm-context="reviewIntro" data-gtm-element="product_link_impression" data-link-type="link" data-merchant="Amazon" data-pid="5541" data-url="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/5541/15770/4/78076/?merchant=Amazon">0.5 mm</a> (V5), <a class="product-link" href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/27485/143532/4/78077/?merchant=Amazon" rel="sponsored noopener" target="_blank" data-gtm-trigger="product_link" data-store="Amazon" data-vars-outbound-link="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/27485/143532/4/78077/?merchant=Amazon" data-vars-store="Amazon" data-gtm-context="reviewIntro" data-gtm-element="product_link_impression" data-link-type="link" data-merchant="Amazon" data-pid="27485" data-url="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/27485/143532/4/78077/?merchant=Amazon">0.7 mm</a> (V7)<br/><strong>Colors:</strong> black, blue, green, pink, purple, red, turquoise, orange, yellow, lime green, navy, burgundy, hunter green, caramel, periwinkle, teal</p><div class="ebb615ab global-cob e1e566ad a9af8aa7 d097cc30" data-scp="callout"><h4 class="d02b79e1 e20b6350" data-scp="callout_label">Also great</h4><div id="callout-intro-5-4" class="fd1ac384" data-scp="callout_item" data-testid="callout"