ball-Jetstream-ballpoint-sample.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=320 320w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Uni-ball-Jetstream-ballpoint-sample.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=320&amp;dpr=1.5 480w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Uni-ball-Jetstream-ballpoint-sample.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=320&amp;dpr=2 640w" width="2048" height="825" class="cf3feb4c c882c9ce size-full wp-image-222198"/></div><figcaption class="wp-caption-text"> The Uni-ball Jetstream RT has dark ink for a ballpoint pen.<!-- --> <span class="wp-caption-text wp-caption-credit">Image: Melanie Pinola</span></figcaption></figure></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0"><p><strong>It comes in a wide range of tip sizes and colors.</strong> If you don’t love the feel of the standard Jetstream RT’s barely there grip or the width of its tip, there are a lot of other options, if you’re willing to venture outside your office-supply store or shop online.</p></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0"><p>The standard 0.7-mm “fine” tip comes in <a class="product-link" href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/200/587/4/78073/?merchant=Amazon" rel="noopener sponsored" target="_blank" data-gtm-trigger="product_link" data-store="Amazon" data-pick-type-id="1" data-vars-outbound-link="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/200/587/4/78073/?merchant=Amazon" data-vars-store="Amazon" data-gtm-context="chapter_our-pick-uni-ball-jetstream-rt" data-gtm-element="product_link_impression" data-link-type="link" data-merchant="Amazon" data-pid="200" data-url="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/200/587/4/78073/?merchant=Amazon">black</a>, <a class="product-link" href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/2846/7611/4/78110/?merchant=Amazon" rel="noopener sponsored" target="_blank" data-gtm-trigger="product_link" data-store="Amazon" data-vars-outbound-link="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/2846/7611/4/78110/?merchant=Amazon" data-vars-store="Amazon" data-gtm-context="chapter_our-pick-uni-ball-jetstream-rt" data-gtm-element="product_link_impression" data-link-type="link" data-merchant="Amazon" data-pid="2846" data-url="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/2846/7611/4/78110/?merchant=Amazon">blue</a>, and a black/blue/red <a class="product-link" href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/2847/7616/4/78111/?merchant=Amazon" rel="noopener sponsored" target="_blank" data-gtm-trigger="product_link" data-store="Amazon" data-vars-outbound-link="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/2847/7616/4/78111/?merchant=Amazon" data-vars-store="Amazon" data-gtm-context="chapter_our-pick-uni-ball-jetstream-rt" data-gtm-element="product_link_impression" data-link-type="link" data-merchant="Amazon" data-pid="2847" data-url="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/2847/7616/4/78111/?merchant=Amazon">multipack</a>. Uni-ball sells a <a class="product-link" href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/2848/7621/4/78112/?merchant=Amazon" rel="noopener sponsored" target="_blank" data-gtm-trigger="product_link" data-store="Amazon" data-vars-outbound-link="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/2848/7621/4/78112/?merchant=Amazon" data-vars-store="Amazon" data-gtm-context="chapter_our-pick-uni-ball-jetstream-rt" data-gtm-element="product_link_impression" data-link-type="link" data-merchant="Amazon" data-pid="2848" data-url="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/2848/7621/4/78112/?merchant=Amazon">1.0-mm “bold” tip</a>, but it produces only a subtle change in line size. Although <a class="product-link" href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/2840/7603/4/37861/?merchant=JetPens" rel="noopener sponsored" target="_blank" data-gtm-trigger="product_link" data-store="JetPens" data-vars-outbound-link="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/2840/7603/4/37861/?merchant=JetPens" data-vars-store="JetPens" data-gtm-context="chapter_our-pick-uni-ball-jetstream-rt" data-gtm-element="product_link_impression" data-link-type="link" data-merchant="JetPens" data-pid="2840" data-url="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/2840/7603/4/37861/?merchant=JetPens">0.5-mm</a> and <a class="product-link" href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/2841/7604/4/37862/?merchant=JetPens" rel="noopener sponsored" target="_blank" data-gtm-trigger="product_link" data-store="JetPens" data-vars-outbound-link="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/2841/7604/4/37862/?merchant=JetPens" data-vars-store="JetPens" data-gtm-context="chapter_our-pick-uni-ball-jetstream-rt" data-gtm-element="product_link_impression" data-link-type="link" data-merchant="JetPens" data-pid="2841" data-url="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/2841/7604/4/37862/?merchant=JetPens">0.38-mm</a> tips do exist, they don’t write as smoothly, according to our experts. Still, if your handwriting is extremely small, you may enjoy their precision. Or you could consider our gel pen picks, the <a href="#also-great-pentel-energel-rtx">Pilot EnerGel RTX</a> and the <a href="#also-great-uni-ball-signo-rt1">Uni-ball Signo RT1</a>, which write smoothly with fine tip sizes.</p></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0"><p><strong>Uniball ink is forgery-resistant and works well on all kinds of paper.</strong> Jetstream pens feature <a href="http://uniball.com.au/uni-super-ink/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Super Ink</a>, which is resistant to removal with acetone as well as more-mundane threats, like water spills and fading. In addition, this ink writes well on glossy paper, including receipts.</p></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0"><h3>Flaws but not dealbreakers</h3></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0"><ul><li>The most consistent complaint among our staff testers was that even though the Jetstream RT produces darker lines than most ballpoint pens, its ink still isn’t as saturated or dark as ink from rollerball and gel pens.</li><li>The Jetstream RT won’t turn heads. If its humble, utilitarian looks aren’t to your liking, some of the <a href="https://www.jetpens.com/blog/uni-jetstream-a-comprehensive-guide/pt/758" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Jetstream variants</a> are arguably better looking. And you can find other pen <a href="https://clickypost.com/blog/2013/7/26/which-karas-kustoms-pen-may-be-right-for-you" rel="noopener" target="_blank">bodies</a> that will take Jetstream refills.</li></ul></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0"><div class="ff31b4af" data-ad-element="outer_ad_container" data-scp="removed"><div class="e5d43c70"><p class="cca4d3b6">Advertisement</p><a href="#after-dfp-ad-chapter-mid-5" class="css-777zgl">SKIP ADVERTISEMENT</a><div class="ad dfp-ad-chapter-mid-5-wrapper css-rfqw0c" id="dfp-ad-chapter-mid-5"></div><div id="after-dfp-ad-chapter-mid-5"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="b6d81848 d47f7b03" id="also-great-uni-jetstream-slim-multi-color" expanded=""><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0 e5f9b502"><h2 class="e823fba7" aria-controls="also-great-uni-jetstream-slim-multi-color-panel" aria-selected="true" role="tab" tabindex="0" data-gtm-element="chapter_heading" data-gtm-trigger="single_chapter" data-chapter-name="Also great: Uni Jetstream Slim Multi-Color" data-expand-close="close" data-chapter-index="5">Also great: Uni Jetstream Slim Multi-Color</h2></div></div><div id="also-great-uni-jetstream-slim-multi-color-panel" class="fa265be5" aria-labelledby="also-great-uni-jetstream-slim-multi-color" aria-hidden="false" role="tabpanel"><div class=" chapter__content-wrapper"><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 bdfcf243"><figure id="atta