6946/Uni-ball-Jetstream-Slim-Multi-Color_20210920-162850_full.jpg" width="570" height="380" class="cf3feb4c c882c9ce" loading="lazy"/></div></a></div><div class="ce2bb787"><div><h3 class="b550f131 e26624a1 a1a87f29"><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/46946/192548/4/135727?merchant=Amazon" class="dfb6b88d" rel="sponsored noreferrer" target="_blank" title="Uni Jetstream Slim Multi-Color" data-gtm-element="callout_product_link_impression" data-link-type="link" data-merchant="Amazon" data-pick-type-id="5" data-pid="46946" data-store="Amazon" data-vars-store="Amazon" data-vars-outbound-link="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/46946/192548/4/135727?merchant=Amazon" data-gtm-trigger="callout_product_link_name" data-scp="callout_product" data-gtm-context="inline">Uni Jetstream Slim Multi-Color</a></h3><h2 class="eafb159a"><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/46946/192548/4/135727?merchant=Amazon" class="c44f6873" rel="sponsored noreferrer" target="_blank" title="A multicolor pen for enhanced note-taking" data-store="Amazon" data-vars-store="Amazon" data-vars-outbound-link="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/46946/192548/4/135727?merchant=Amazon" data-gtm-trigger="callout_product_link_title" data-scp="callout_title" data-pid="46946" data-gtm-context="inline">A multicolor pen for enhanced note-taking</a></h2></div><p class="ec57f3ca" data-scp="callout_description">This pen is as slim as a typical ballpoint, and you can switch between writing with black, blue, and red ink—without having to carry multiple pens.</p><div class="dded66b7"><div data-scp="removed"><h4 class="efa3259d">Buying Options</h4><div class="b279b202 product-pricebox-0" data-source-id-order="0" data-country-code="US"><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/46946/192548/4/135727?merchant=Amazon" class="b50e01ee" data-gtm-element="callout_buy_button_impression" data-link-type="button" data-merchant="Amazon" data-pick-type-id="5" data-pid="46946" data-store="Amazon" data-vars-store="Amazon" data-vars-outbound-link="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/46946/192548/4/135727?merchant=Amazon" rel="sponsored noreferrer" target="_blank" data-gtm-context="inline" data-gtm-trigger="callout_product_link_button"><span>$12</span> from <span>Amazon</span></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0"><p>Most multicolor pens—including the nostalgic <a class="product-link" href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/46958/174767/4/135751/?merchant=Amazon" rel="noopener sponsored" target="_blank" data-gtm-trigger="product_link" data-store="Amazon" data-vars-outbound-link="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/46958/174767/4/135751/?merchant=Amazon" data-vars-store="Amazon" data-gtm-context="chapter_also-great-uni-jetstream-slim-multi-color" data-gtm-element="product_link_impression" data-link-type="link" data-merchant="Amazon" data-pid="46958" data-url="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/46958/174767/4/135751/?merchant=Amazon">BIC 4-Color pen</a> from the ’70s and ’80s—have thick bodies that can feel unwieldy. Not so the <a class="product-link" href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/46946/192548/4/135791/?merchant=Amazon" rel="noopener sponsored" target="_blank" data-gtm-trigger="product_link" data-store="Amazon" data-pick-type-id="5" data-vars-outbound-link="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/46946/192548/4/135791/?merchant=Amazon" data-vars-store="Amazon" data-gtm-context="chapter_also-great-uni-jetstream-slim-multi-color" data-gtm-element="product_link_impression" data-link-type="link" data-merchant="Amazon" data-pid="46946" data-url="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/46946/192548/4/135791/?merchant=Amazon">Uni Jetstream Slim Multi-Color</a>, an elegant pen that’s the size of a single-ink ballpoint pen, like the <a href="#our-pick-uni-ball-jetstream-rt">Jetstream RT</a>.</p></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0"><p><strong>It’s a color-changing pen without the bulk.</strong> For annotating documents or color-coding your notes, you can switch between black, blue, and red. And the ink is as smooth-flowing and consistent as ink in other Jetstream pens.</p></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0"><p>We found this pen’s soft rubber grip comfortable to hold, and we thought the subtle pattern on the monochromatic body was aesthetically pleasing. In our tests, switching between colors was seamless. And because of this pen’s size and versatility, we think it’s a great option to carry every day.</p></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 bdfcf243"><figure id="attachment_222200" class="wp-caption alignnone"><div class="ec5f8867 global_chapter__arp_image b71ff2c5"><img loading="lazy" alt="A person holding the Uni-ball Jetstream Slim Multi-Color." src="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multicolor.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=320" data-src="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multicolor.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=1024" data-srcset="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multicolor.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multicolor.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=1024&amp;dpr=1.5 1536w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multicolor.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=1024&amp;dpr=2 2048w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multicolor.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=980 980w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multicolor.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=980&amp;dpr=1.5 1470w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multicolor.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=980&amp;dpr=2 1960w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multicolor.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=768 768w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multicolor.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=768&amp;dpr=1.5 1152w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multicolor.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=768&amp;dpr=2 1536w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multicolor.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=480 480w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multicolor.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=480&amp;dpr=1.5 720w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multicolor.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=480&amp;dpr=2 960w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multicolor.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=320 320w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multicolor.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=320&amp;dpr=1.5 480w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multicolor.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=320&amp;dpr=2 640w" width="2048" height="1365" class="cf3feb4c c882c9ce size-full wp-image-222200"/></div><figcaption class="wp-caption-text"> You might not be able to tell just from glancing at this minimalist-looking pen that it can write in three colors.<!-- --> <span class="wp-caption-text wp-caption-credit">Photo: Melanie Pinola</span></figcaption></figure></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0"><p><strong>It writes better than other multicolor pens.</strong> After testing two other multicolor options, we found that the Jetstream Slim Multi-Color offered the best writing experience overall. The 0.5-mm version we tested laid down crisp, smooth lines that never skipped or blobbed.</p></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 bdfcf243"><figure id="attachment_222201" class="wp-caption alignnone"><div class="ec5f8867 global_chapter__arp_image b71ff2c5"><img loading="lazy" alt="A writing sample produced with the Uni-ball Jetstream Slim Multi-Color, showing black, red, and blue ink." src="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multi-color.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=320" data-src="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multi-color.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=1024" data-srcset="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multi-color.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multi-color.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=1024&amp;dpr=1.5 1536w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multi-color.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=1024&amp;dpr=2 2048w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multi-color.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=980 980w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multi-color.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=980&amp;dpr=1.5 1470w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multi-color.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=980&amp;dpr=2 1960w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multi-color.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=768 768w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multi-color.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=768&amp;dpr=1.5 1152w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multi-color.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=768&amp;dpr=2 1536w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multi-color.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=480 480w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multi-color.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=480&amp;dpr=1.5 720w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multi-color.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=480&amp;dpr=2 960w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multi-color.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=320 320w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multi-color.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=320&amp;dpr=1.5 480w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Uni-ball-Jetstream-multi-color.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=320&amp;dpr=2 640w" width="2048" height="1466" class="cf3feb4c c882c9ce size-full wp-image-222201"/></div><figcaption class="wp-caption-text"> The Uni-ball Slim Multi-Color ballpoint puts down solid lines in three colors.<!-- --> <span class="wp-caption-text wp-caption-credit">Image: Melanie Pinola</span></figcaption></figure></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0"><p><strong>It’s easy to change colors.</strong> This pen’s angled, wide knocks made switching ink colors easier than the tinier knocks on the <a href="#the-competition">Pilot Hi-Tec-C Coleto</a> or the <a href="#other-good-pens">Uni Jetstream 4&amp;1</a>.</p></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0"><p>The Jetstream Slim Multi-Color’s knocks also operated smoothly, with a satisfying click, and they held their position (unlike the Hi-Tec-C Coleto’s knocks).</p></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0"><p><strong>It’s comfortable to hold.</strong> Thanks to its relatively light weight and soft grip section, the Jetstream Slim Multi-Color doesn’t wear out your hand during extended writing periods.</p></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0"><p><strong>It looks great, too.</strong> We appreciated the subtle, stylish, light colors the pen comes in (including white, pink, mint green, and lavender).</p></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0"><p><strong>It has one notable flaw.</strong> Our main complaint about the design is that the color of each ink is imprinted on the body of the pen, not on the knock. So if you reload the pen with <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=obHBA9-cEjw" rel="noopener" target="_blank">different colors or gel inks</a>, you’ll have to remember which knock belongs to which color.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="b6d81848 d47f7b03" id="also-great-pilot-dr-grip-center-of-gravity" expanded=""><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0 e5f9b502"><h2 class="e823fba7" aria-controls="also-great-pilot-dr-grip-center-of-gravity-panel" aria-selected="true" role="tab" tabindex="0" data-gtm-element="chapter_heading" data-gtm-trigger="single_chapter" data-chapter-name="Also great: Pilot Dr. Grip Center of Gravity" data-expand-close="close" data-chapter-index="6">Also great: Pilot Dr. Grip Center of Gravity</h2></div></div><div id="also-great-pilot-dr-grip-center-of-gravity-panel" class="fa265be5" aria-labelledby="also-g