" data-vars-store="Amazon" data-gtm-context="chapter_also-great-pilot-dr-grip-center-of-gravity" data-gtm-element="product_link_impression" data-link-type="link" data-merchant="Amazon" data-pid="46766" data-url="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/46766/198200/4/135754/?merchant=Amazon">Dr. Grip Limited</a>’s did), and it skipped less than the <a class="product-link" href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/490/1372/4/135755/?merchant=Amazon" rel="noopener sponsored" target="_blank" data-gtm-trigger="product_link" data-store="Amazon" data-vars-outbound-link="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/490/1372/4/135755/?merchant=Amazon" data-vars-store="Amazon" data-gtm-context="chapter_also-great-pilot-dr-grip-center-of-gravity" data-gtm-element="product_link_impression" data-link-type="link" data-merchant="Amazon" data-pid="490" data-url="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/490/1372/4/135755/?merchant=Amazon">Jetstream Alpha-Gel</a>’s ink.</p></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 bdfcf243"><figure id="attachment_222204" class="wp-caption alignnone"><div class="ec5f8867 global_chapter__arp_image b71ff2c5"><img loading="lazy" alt="A writing sample produced using the Pilot Dr. Grip Center of Gravity." src="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Pilot-Dr-Grip.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=320" data-src="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Pilot-Dr-Grip.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=1024" data-srcset="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Pilot-Dr-Grip.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Pilot-Dr-Grip.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=1024&amp;dpr=1.5 1536w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Pilot-Dr-Grip.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=1024&