e to hold.<!-- --> <span class="wp-caption-text wp-caption-credit">Image: Melanie Pinola</span></figcaption></figure></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0"><p><strong>The squishy grip does have one downside.</strong> The rubber grip collects lint, which is an annoyance. But that is a small price to pay for a pen that writes so well and so comfortably.</p></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0"><div class="ff31b4af" data-ad-element="outer_ad_container" data-scp="removed"><div class="e5d43c70"><p class="cca4d3b6">Advertisement</p><a href="#after-dfp-ad-chapter-mid-6" class="css-777zgl">SKIP ADVERTISEMENT</a><div class="ad dfp-ad-chapter-mid-6-wrapper css-rfqw0c" id="dfp-ad-chapter-mid-6"></div><div id="after-dfp-ad-chapter-mid-6"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="b6d81848 d47f7b03" id="also-great-pilot-precise-v5-rt" expanded=""><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0 e5f9b502"><h2 class="e823fba7" aria-controls="also-great-pilot-precise-v5-rt-panel" aria-selected="true" role="tab" tabindex="0" data-gtm-element="chapter_heading" data-gtm-trigger="single_chapter" data-chapter-name="Also great: Pilot Precise V5 RT" data-expand-close="close" data-chapter-index="7">Also great: Pilot Precise V5 RT</h2></div></div><div id="also-great-pilot-precise-v5-rt-panel" class="fa265be5" aria-labelledby="also-great-pilot-precise-v5-rt" aria-hidden="false" role="tabpanel"><div class=" chapter__content-wrapper"><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 bdfcf243"><figure id="attachment_222417" class="wp-caption alignnone"><div class="ec5f8867 global_chapter__arp_image b71ff2c5"><img loading="lazy" alt="An inexpensive pen with dark ink, the Pilot Precise V5 RT, shown on a notebook." src="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-6471-1.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=320" data-src="https://cdn