/wirecutter/out/link/46763/174456/4/135730?merchant=Amazon" data-gtm-trigger="callout_product_link_title" data-scp="callout_title" data-pid="46763" data-gtm-context="inline">A smudge-free gel pen with many color and tip-size options</a></h2></div><p class="ec57f3ca" data-scp="callout_description">This pen produces dark, crisp lines, and it’s available in a wide range of colors and tip sizes to suit various writing preferences.</p><div class="dded66b7"><div data-scp="removed"><h4 class="efa3259d">Buying Options</h4><div class="b279b202 product-pricebox-0" data-source-id-order="0" data-country-code="US"><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/46763/174456/4/135730?merchant=Amazon" class="b50e01ee" data-gtm-element="callout_buy_button_impression" data-link-type="button" data-merchant="Amazon" data-pick-type-id="5" data-pid="46763" data-store="Amazon" data-vars-store="Amazon" data-vars-outbound-link="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/46763/174456/4/135730?merchant=Amazon" rel="sponsored noreferrer" target="_blank" data-gtm-context="inline" data-gtm-trigger="callout_product_link_button"><span>$14</span> from <span>Amazon</span><br/><span>(pack of five)</span></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0"><p>If you’re seeking an especially versatile pen, the <a class="product-link" href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/46763/174456/4/135739/?merchant=Amazon" rel="noopener sponsored" target="_blank" data-gtm-trigger="product_link" data-store="Amazon" data-pick-type-id="5" data-vars-outbound-link="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/46763/174456/4/135739/?merchant=Amazon" data-vars-store="Amazon" data-gtm-context="chapter_also-great-pentel-energel-rtx" data-gtm-element="product_link_impression" data-link-type="link" data-merchant="Amazon" data-pid="46763" data-url="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/out/link/46763/174456/4/135739/?merchant=Amazon">Pentel EnerGel RTX</a> has the most refill options of the pens we tested: There are over a dozen ink colors and four tip sizes (from 0.3 mm to 1.0 mm) to choose from.</p></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 cdde21c0"><p><strong>Its gel ink is crisp and smudge-free.</strong> This pen writes with crisp, dark lines similar to those of the <a href="#also-great-pilot-precise-v5-rt">Pilot Precise V5 RT</a>, but it never smudged in our tests. It was our left-handed tester’s top pick because of how fast the ink dried.</p></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 bdfcf243"><figure id="attachment_222210" class="wp-caption alignnone"><div class="ec5f8867 global_chapter__arp_image b71ff2c5"><img loading="lazy" alt="A writing sample produced using the Pentel EnerGel RTX." src="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Pentel-EnerGel.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=320" data-src="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Pentel-EnerGel.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=1024" data-srcset="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Pentel-EnerGel.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Pentel-EnerGel.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=1024&amp;dpr=1.5 1536w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Pentel-EnerGel.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=1024&amp;dpr=2 2048w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Pentel-EnerGel.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=980 980w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Pentel-EnerGel.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=980&amp;dpr=1.5 1470w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-samples-Pentel-EnerGel.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;wid