t also rattles a bit more than our other picks.</p></div></div></div><div><div class="a1497183"><div class="f21e64f1 b5823c44 bdfcf243"><figure id="attachment_222211" class="wp-caption alignnone"><div class="ec5f8867 global_chapter__arp_image b71ff2c5"><img loading="lazy" alt="The The Pentel EnerGel RTX shown next to the Uni-ball Signo RT1." src="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-6533.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=320" data-src="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-6533.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=1024" data-srcset="https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-6533.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-6533.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=1024&amp;dpr=1.5 1536w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-6533.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=1024&amp;dpr=2 2048w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-6533.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=980 980w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-6533.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=980&amp;dpr=1.5 1470w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-6533.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=980&amp;dpr=2 1960w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-6533.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=768 768w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-6533.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=768&amp;dpr=1.5 1152w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-6533.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=768&amp;dpr=2 1536w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-6533.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=480 480w,https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-6533.jpg?auto=webp&amp;quality=75&amp;width=480&amp;