 your hand during extended writing periods. It looks great, too. We appreciated the subtle, stylish, light colors the pen comes in (including white, pink, mint green, and lavender). It has one notable flaw. Our main complaint about the design is that the color of each ink is imprinted on the body of the pen, not on the knock. So if you reload the pen with different colors or gel inks, you’ll have to remember which knock belongs to which color.","title":"Also great: Uni Jetstream Slim Multi-Color","slug":"also-great-uni-jetstream-slim-multi-color","chapterModifiedDate":null,"chapterPublishedDate":null,"faqs":null,"footnotes":null,"sources":null},{"body":[{"type":"tag","name":"shortcode-caption","attribs":{"id":"attachment_222202","align":"alignnone","width":"2048"},"children":[{"type":"tag","name":"img","attribs":{"class":"alignnone size-full wp-image-222202","src":"https://cdn.thewirecutter.com/wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-6513.jpg","alt":"The best pen for ergonomics, the Pilot Dr. Grip Center of Gravity, shown on a notebook.","width":"2048","height":"1365","noInlineStyles":true,"postType":"review"},"children":[],"dbData":{"productionCDN":true,"source":"wp-content/media/2021/09/pens-2048px-6513.jpg"}},{"data":" ","type":"text"},{"data":" ","type":"comment"}],"dbData":{"credit":"Photo: Michael Hession"}},{"data":"\n","type":"text"},{"type":"tag","name":"shortcode-callout","attribs":{"type":"alternate","id":"2"},"children":[],"dbData":{"ribbon":"Also great","callouts":[{"name":"Pilot Dr. Grip Center of Gravity","title":"The most ergonomic pen","images":{"full":"https://d1b5h9psu9yexj.cloudfront.net/46948/Pilot-Dr--Grip-Center-of-Gravity_20210920-162900_full.jpg"},"description":"If you experience hand strain or fatigue while writing with slim pens, this pen’s large, soft grip and balanced weight distribution can make writing more comfortable.","notGreat":0,"ribbon":"Also great","pickTypeId":5,"referenceId":135728,"sources":[{"id":174757,"price":{"raw":869,"form